# Design System Rules

Use this guide to translate Figma MCP outputs into this repo's design system. Follow it for all UI changes.

## Token Definitions

- **Source of truth:** CSS custom properties in `app/globals.css`.
- **Usage pattern:** Tailwind utility classes with CSS variables, e.g. `bg-[var(--background-main-default)]` and `text-[length:var(--size-base)]`.
- **Common aliases:** Some tokens are duplicated with slash and dash naming (ex: `--size/base` and `--size-base`). Prefer the **slash** naming in new code when available.
- **Focus shadows:** Use `--shadow/accessibility/*` tokens and apply them only on focus-visible states.

## Token Categories

### Colors
- **Background:** `--background/main/default`, `--card/color/bg/default`, `--table/color/bg/*`
- **Border:** `--border/main/default`, `--card/color/border/default`, `--input/color/border/*`
- **Text:** `--text/main/default`, `--text/subtle/default`, `--input/color/fg/*`
- **Status:** `--badge/color/*/success|warning|danger|neutral`, `--banner/color/*/info|warning|danger|success`

### Typography
- **Sizes:** `--size-base` (16px), `--size-small` (14px), `--size-caption` (12px)
- **Line heights:** `--leading-base` (24px), `--leading-small` (20px), `--leading-caption` (16px)
- **Weights:** `--weight-regular` (400), `--weight-semibold` (600)
- **Heading sizes:** `--font-h1-size` through `--font-h6-size`

### Spacing & Dimensions
- **Spacing scale:** `--space-1` through `--space-12`
- **Component dimensions:** `--dimensions/height` (56px), `--dimensions/radii` (8px), `--dimensions/padding/*`
- **Icon dimensions:** `--icon/dimension/width/base` (20px), `--icon/dimension/height/base` (20px)

## Component Library

- **UI components live in:** `ui/`
- **Pattern:** stateless React components with props, using Tailwind + CSS variables.
- **Exports:** `ui/index.ts` is the public surface; add new primitives there.

## Component Token Mapping

### Card
- Background: `--card/color/bg/default`
- Border: `--card/color/border/default`
- Border radius: `--card/dimensions/radii`
- Padding: `--card/dimensions/padding/inline`, `--card/dimensions/padding/block`

### Badge
- Padding: `--badge/dimensions/padding/inline`, `--badge/dimensions/padding/block`
- Border radius: `--badge/dimensions/radii` (pill shape: 999px)
- Colors per variant: `--badge/color/bg|fg|border/{variant}`

### Banner
- Padding: `--banner/dimensions/padding`
- Border radius: `--banner/dimensions/radii`
- Colors per variant: `--banner/color/bg|fg|border/{variant}`

### Button
- Height: `--button-height-lg` (48px), `--button-height-sm` (32px)
- Border radius: `--button-radius` (64px)
- Colors per variant/sentiment: `--button-{sentiment}-{variant}-{state}`

### Input/FieldInput
- Height: `--input/dimensions/height` (56px)
- Border radius: `--input/dimensions/radii` (8px)
- Padding: `--input/dimensions/padding/inline`
- Colors: `--input/color/bg/*`, `--input/color/border/*`, `--input/color/fg/*`

### Select/FieldSelect
- All tokens prefixed with `--select-*`
- Focus shadow: `--select-shadow-focus`
- Menu shadow: `--select-shadow-menu`

### Switch
- All tokens prefixed with `--switch/*`
- Dimensions: `--switch/dimensions/width` (56px), `--switch/dimensions/height` (32px)

### Checkbox
- All tokens prefixed with `--checkbox/*`
- Dimensions: `--checkbox/input/dimensions/width|height` (16px)

### Radio
- All tokens prefixed with `--radio/*`
- Dimensions: `--radio/input/dimensions/width|height` (16px)

### Table
- Header background: `--table/color/bg/header`
- Body background: `--table/color/bg/body`
- Hover: `--table/color/bg/hover`
- Border: `--table/color/border/default`

### Modal
- Overlay: `--modal/color/overlay`
- Background: `--modal/color/bg/default`
- Border radius: `--modal/dimensions/radii`
- Max width: `--modal/dimensions/max-width`

### AppShell
- Sidebar width: `--shell/sidebar/width`
- Colors: `--shell/color/bg/sidebar|main|header`
- Padding: `--shell/dimensions/padding`

### Link
- Primary color: `--link-primary`
- Hover color: `--link-primary-hover`
- Focus color: `--link-primary-focus`

## Frameworks & Libraries

- **Framework:** Next.js App Router (`app/`).
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS with design tokens defined in `app/globals.css`.
- **State:** React hooks; no external UI libs.

## Asset Management

- **Icons & SVGs:** Stored as URLs (often localhost) in component files. Follow existing patterns (const string URL + `<img src=...>`).
- **Local assets:** `public/illustrations/` used directly via `/illustrations/...`.

## Icon System

- **Usage:** Inline `<img>` tags with fixed dimensions and CSS variable sizing.
- **Naming:** `iconSomething` or `imgSomething` constants per component.
- **Icon sizes:** Use `--icon/dimension/width|height/base` (20px) or `--icon/dimension/width|height/caption` (16px)

## Styling Approach

- **Tailwind utilities + CSS variables:** Use `var(--token-name)` inside Tailwind brackets
- **Tokens over raw colors:** Never hardcode colors, always use CSS vars
- **Accessibility:** Keep `aria-*` attributes in control components (switch/checkbox/radio)
- **Focus states:** Use `--shadow/accessibility/*` tokens for focus rings

## Project Structure

- **UI primitives:** `ui/`
- **Feature pages:** `app/**/page.tsx`
- **State/context:** `contexts/`
- **Domain models:** `domain/`
- **Tests:** `tests/ui/` for Playwright UI tests

## Figma MCP Components (Selection)

Always use the following primitives for selection controls and keep them aligned to Figma tokens/states:

- `FieldSwitch` (`ui/FieldSwitch.tsx`)
- `FieldCheckbox` (`ui/FieldCheckbox.tsx`)
- `FieldRadioGroup` (`ui/FieldRadioGroup.tsx`)

If a screen uses a switch/checkbox/radiobutton, replace custom markup with these primitives or align indicators with the same tokens and assets.

## UI Test Requirement

For every task that modifies UI components or screens, add/extend a Playwright UI test that verifies:
1. Component visibility
2. Correct CSS properties from design tokens (dimensions, colors, spacing)
3. Interactive states (hover, focus, disabled) when applicable

Test file location: `tests/ui/design-system.spec.ts`
